    <h3>Accountex silent film</h3>
    <p>Accountex is like Glastonbury for accountants. Every Accountex FreeAgent
      has a stand. On this stand there's televisions and when they're not
      being used for showing off the FreeAgent app they display a silent video
      explaining what we do and how great FreeAgent is</p>
    <p>This was my second time creating the video for Accountex. This year we had a
      slight rebrand of our accountants' facing marketing, so while not much of the
      content had changed the overall look changed quite significantly.</p>
    <p>
      In this version I was able to use our existing illustrations and animate them
      to convey our functionality and features.
