        <h3>Resources for accountants</h3>
        <p>At FreeAgent we had a lot of disparate content online but no central hub for it.
          Working with marketing we came up with one central page that would host
          all the resources we had that were relevant to accountants,
          including white papers, webcasts and infographics. </p>
        <p>
          The resources page uses Middleman and draws from a YAML file to
          populate the page. This was a good opportunity to sharpen my Ruby
          skills. I’m no software engineer but I now know a thing or two!
          Because it draws from a YAML file it’s easy for anybody to update,
          as long as they have some copy and an image to represent their resource.
        </p>
